    "attributes": {
        "action": "Disregard compensation payments for means-tested benefits",
        "additional_details": "We have been awarded a sum in compensation, and due to the laws surrounding the payment not being a \u201cpersonal injury\u201d, we will lose access to our means-tested benefits. We will then have to use the compensation payment for rent, bills etc, instead of putting it away for our children\u2019s future.",
        "background": "Myself and my partner recently lost our beautiful daughter Violet at 8 weeks of age. We are fighting every day, and will not stop fighting in Violet's memory, until something changes. ",
